Reproducing our parameter estimates

Source: vignettes/reproducibility.Rmd
reproducibility.Rmd

Although all parameter values in the model can be changed by the user, the package loads with baseline parameter values. All R scripts for parameter estimation are in the data-raw directory on GitHub, and all estimates are built using the Makefile found here.

Developed by Jeroen P. Jansen, Devin Incerti.
